snippet.title: Our Kind of Entertainment
snippet.description:
I created this YouTube channel with the purpose of discussing television, music, movies and other forms of entertainment that I find interesting. My hope is that you enjoy the time you spend watching my content. Feel free to engage with other subscribers by commenting on my videos to share your thoughts and opinions. Make sure you subscribe to keep up with my content as it gets uploaded to the channel.

Don't hesitate to reach out to me with any recommendations on new content to cover.
